OL,11,     Fcasualty department.
OL,12,G2100 999: Critical Condition
OL,13,     FHaving plummeted 15 feet onto
OL,14,     Fconcrete, Michael is rushed into
OL,15,     Fresus with a significant
OL,16,     Flaceration to his head. And a
OL,17,     Fdriver has a crushed leg after
OL,18,     Fbeing run over by his own van.
